data.description: This home offers seller-paid rate buy-down so you can settle in for the holidays.  Relish LAKE LIFE with the convenience of the city.  Enjoy the beautiful lake from your patio or while sipping your morning beverage when looking out your dining room window.  The dining room features a beautiful trey ceiling as well as the ceiling in your large primary bedroom.  The primary bathroom features a separate shower and bathtub, double vanity sinks, private water closet, and TWO walk-in closets.  The home has been upgraded with ceramic tile in the kitchen, breakfast nook/office, and laundry room.  The kitchen features a stunning back splash.  The back patio has been enclosed with a beautiful black wrought iron fence.  Enjoy fireworks every 4th of July from the Historic American Village while sitting on your front porch.
